			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2512288">
									

<p>The &quot;Massy's Big Chance&quot; style &quot;misspelled for humor&quot; sections aren't very entertaining, because they're just&#8230; misspelled. There's an inkling of a cool story with the Glory Hole crossover, but that never amounts to anything.</p>
<p>The climax with the images made me feel uncomfortable. Getting harassed sexually over the internet, especially by a person who has gradually earned your trust is&#8230; well, that just makes me feel anxious.</p>
<p>Verdict: Downvote.</p>

